c: 46
v: 8
t: "Or they say: \"He fabricated/cut and split it.\" Say: \"If I fabricated/cut and split it, so you do not own/possess for me from God a thing. He is more knowledgeable with what you rush/hurry in it, enough/sufficient with Him (as) a witness/testifier between me and between you, and He is the forgiving, the merciful"